---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { profile } from '../data/profile';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="关于 YZH。" path="/about">
  <section class="about-hero shell">
    <p class="eyebrow fade-in">About</p>
    <h1 class="fade-in fade-in-delay-1">你好，我是<br /><span class="highlight">{profile.name}</span>。</h1>
    <p class="hero-lead fade-in fade-in-delay-2">{profile.intro}</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section shell about-grid">
    <article class="statement fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
      <p class="drop-cap">
        我喜欢把模糊的问题整理成可执行的结构——先理解真实材料和使用流程，再选择足够简单的工程方案完成实现与验证。代码不是目的，解决问题才是。
      </p>
      <p>
        目前专注于 Java 后端与 AI 应用方向，同时对系统设计、工程效率和前端体验保持持续的探索兴趣。
        这里的项目、文章和笔记会随着实践持续变化。相比一份固定介绍，我更希望它成为能够看见成长过程的公开档案。
      </p>
    </article>

    <aside class="info-card glass-card fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
      <div class="fact">
        <span>📍 Location</span>
        <strong>{profile.location}</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="fact">
        <span>🔭 Focus</span>
        <strong>Software Engineering</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="fact">
        <span>🟢 Status</span>
        <strong>Open to collaboration</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="fact">
        <span>🎓 Education</span>
        <strong>HDU · CS · 2024–2028</strong>
      </div>
      <a class="button-link" href={`mailto:${profile.email}`} style="width:100%; margin-top: 8px;">
        发送邮件 →
      </a>
    </aside>
  </section>

  <div class="section-divider shell" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <section class="section shell now-section">
    <h2 class="section-heading">当前在做</h2>
    <ul class="now-list">
      {profile.now.map((item) => <li class="fade-in">{item}</li>)}
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    padding-block: clamp(64px, 10vw, 120px) clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px);
  }

  .about-hero h1 {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Georgia, 'Songti SC', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5.2rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.06;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  .highlight {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .hero-lead {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 24px 0 0;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.12rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(280px, 360px);
    gap: clamp(48px, 8vw, 100px);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .statement {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .drop-cap::first-letter {
    float: left;
    margin-right: 12px;
    font-family: Georgia, 'Songti SC', serif;
    font-size: 3.6rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 0.8;
    color: var(--blue);
  }

  .statement > p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.95;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .statement > p + p {
    margin-top: 1.4em;
  }

  .info-card {
    position: sticky;
    top: 64px;
    align-self: start;
    padding: 26px 28px;
  }

  .fact {
    display: grid;
    gap: 5px;
    padding-block: 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .fact:last-of-type {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .fact span {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .fact strong {
    font-size: 0.94rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .now-section h2 {
    margin: 0 0 28px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .now-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .now-list li {
    position: relative;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    font-size: 0.93rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    transition: all 200ms ease;
  }

  .now-list li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: -8px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    color: var(--blue);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: all 200ms ease;
  }

  .now-list li:hover {
    border-color: var(--blue);
    color: var(--text);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    transform: translateX(4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }

  .now-list li:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
    left: -10px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .info-card {
      position: static;
    }

    .now-list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
